casebody.data:
No. 613. Liverpool, Brazil and River Plate Steam Navigation Company, Limited, et al., Petitioners, v. The Steamship Eagle Point, etc. March 12, 1906. Mr. Harrington Putnam, Mr. Charles C. Burlingham, Mr: H. G. Ward and Mr. George H. Emerson for petitioners. Mr. Wilhelmus Mynderse :for respondent.

Petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied.
